sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant Frontend
  participant Gateway
  participant AuthService
  participant OrderService
  participant Database

  User->>Frontend: Click "Place Order"
  activate Frontend
  Frontend->>Gateway: POST /orders
  activate Gateway
  Gateway->>AuthService: Validate JWT
  AuthService-->>Gateway: Token valid, user=42

  alt Order valid
    Gateway->>OrderService: CreateOrder(userId=42, items=[...])
    activate OrderService
    OrderService->>Database: INSERT order
    Database-->>OrderService: order_id=9001
    OrderService-->>Gateway: Order created
    deactivate OrderService
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 201 {"order_id": 9001}
  else Validation failed
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 400 Bad Request
  end

  deactivate Gateway
  Frontend-->>User: Show confirmation
  deactivate Frontend

  Note over Frontend,Gateway: All calls use TLS 1.3
